de.ra.coc.Clan

Class Clan

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ra.coc.Clan.Clan

  • public class Clan
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the Clash of Clan's single Clan. This class requires clan's tag and the JSON Web Token to connect to the Clash of Clan server to retrieve the Clan'S information. To get the JSON Web Token see https://developer.clashofclans.com/

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Clan(java.lang.String JWToken, java.lang.String ClanTag)
      Initialize newly constructed Clan with the passed JSON Web Token and clan's tag and retrieves the clan's information from the Clash of Clan server.

      • Clan

        public Clan(java.lang.String JWToken,
            java.lang.String ClanTag)
     throws COCServerConnectionException,
            java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException,
            InvalidClanTagException
        Initialize newly constructed Clan with the passed JSON Web Token and clan's tag and retrieves the clan's information from the Clash of Clan server. To get the JSON Web Token see https://developer.clashofclans.com/
        Parameters:
        JWToken - JSON Web Token.
        ClanTag - Clan's tag.
        Throws:
        COCServerConnectionException - If the connection to Clash of Clan server is failed.
        InvalidClanTagException - If the given clan tag contains invalid character or not found in Clash of Clans server.
        java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException - If the given player tag is failed to encode to avoid taint-style vulnerabilities.
